{"_path":"/","_dir":"","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"About","description":"Full-Stack Developer","layout":"default","head":{"title":"Josh Avrick"},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"hero","props":{"image":"/glacier.jpg"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"template","props":{"v-slot:title":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Full-Stack Developer"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"template","props":{"v-slot:description":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JavaScript / TypeScript developer, currently based in Alexandria, VA."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I have five years of "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshavrick/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"professional experience"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and an even longer history of toiling away on fairly niche "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/JHAvrick","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"pet projects"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I know all the "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://survey.stackoverflow.co/2023/#most-popular-technologies-language-prof","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hottest tech"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and all the "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gabe_Newell","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hottest people"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pictured"}]},{"type":"text","value":": Squinting on "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.visiticeland.com/article/snaefellsjokull-national-park","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Snaefellsjokull Glacier"}]},{"type":"text","value":" in Iceland, where I go for all my headshots."}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"They say if you stand in front of a mirror in a dark room and whisper "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bing.com/videos/riverview/relatedvideo?&q=developers+developers+developers&&mid=7A55BAD6B4659CBD983D7A55BAD6B4659CBD983D&&FORM=VRDGAR","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"developers, developers, developers\""}]},{"type":"text","value":" you can summon the ghost of XP-era "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://media.vanityfair.com/photos/54ca8f90f547ce3c06e1c9b9/master/pass/image.jpg","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steve Ballmer"}]},{"type":"text","value":". I'm shaking just thinking about it, and to be honest, I'm still kind of reeling from when that "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://english.stackexchange.com/a/65812","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"wizard"}]},{"type":"text","value":" cursed me with waking visions of "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Bob","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Microsoft Bob"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Anyways, if you'd like to get in touch with me you can try speaking my name thrice into a mirror, or you could just use this blog's "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/contact"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"contact form"}]},{"type":"text","value":", email me at "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"mailto:josh@avrick.dev"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"josh@avrick.dev"}]},{"type":"text","value":" (preferred), or send me a message on "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshavrick/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LinkedIn"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In the meantime, let me give you a birds-eye-view of my recent work. You see, when I'm not memorizing passages from my copy of "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Mythical_Man-Month","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"The Mythical Man Month\""}]},{"type":"text","value":", I am working full-time at a company called "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.alertus.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alertus"}]},{"type":"text","value":", based in Baltimore, where we build emergency alerting software, hardware, you name it, "},{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"the works"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Here is an incomplete list of the projects for which I have have been owner or participant:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mass Notification Recipient, a Chrome Extension"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - This early project involved the design and development of a new product from scratch, a Chrome extension, which could be deployed by enterprise customers via GSuite (now Google Workspace) or GPO, usually to a fleet of Chromebooks. "}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IPAWS Activation and Reporting, an Interface"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - If you've never heard of "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.fema.gov/emergency-managers/practitioners/integrated-public-alert-warning-system","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IPAWS"}]},{"type":"text","value":", it's FEMA's national alerting system which is responsible for those AMBER Alerts you keep ignoring. FEMA provides the system, but the rest is kind of an \"assembly required\" type of deal. This project involved some fairly complex data modeling and state management, mapping the UI to FEMA's custom "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap/v1.1/ipaws-profile/v1.0/cap-v1.1-ipaws-profile-v1.0.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CAP Specification"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Props, State, Components, Oh My "}]},{"type":"text","value":" - I've written somewhere between dozens and trillions (inclusive) of custom components ranging from base-level \"core\" components to veritable mini-applications in and of themselves. I am well-versed in "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://vuejs.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vue.js"}]},{"type":"text","value":", I know my way around "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://react.dev/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"React"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and I've even cast a sideways glance or two at "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://svelte.dev/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Svelte"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Migrations and Modernizations, a Myriad"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Over the course of my tenure I have participated in a system-wide frontend redesign, the adoption of modern JavaScript tooling, championed the use of established "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.patterns.dev/#patterns","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"design patterns"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and helped to create and document a consistent design language."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Oh CRUD"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - I've created, read, updated, and deleted so many CRUD applications my head is spinning. I'm the cream of the CRUDS, you might say, and we all know "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.wwe.com/videos/macho-man-randy-savage-claims-he-s-the-cream-of-the-crop-prime-time-wrestling-may-11-1987","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"cream rises to the top"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This is really just scratching the surface, the first things that popped into my head. If you'd like to hear about the more technical aspects, feel free to reach out and we can talk shop."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alright, that's all I've got for now. Here are a few other images taken in various locations, all shot with a "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://fujifilm-x.com/en-us/products/cameras/x-t4/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fuji XT-4"}]},{"type":"text","value":" using an 18-55mm lens."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"gallery","props":{":images":"[\"/glacier2.png\",\"/beacon.webp\",\"landscape.png\",\"/swans.webp\",\"/ice.png\",\"/lighthouse.png\"]"},"children":[]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:1.index.md","_source":"content","_file":"1.index.md","_extension":"md"}